    "description": {
      "value": "<p>While in this stance, whenever you make an attack action, attack of opportunity, or additional attack granted by a class feature or talent with an unarmed strike, you may spend an attack of opportunity to take a 5-foot step immediately after the attack as a free action that can be taken even outside of your normal turn. You may make 5-foot steps in this manner even if you have already moved for the round. <strong>Associated Feat:</strong> Circling Mongoose.</p>\n",
